            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間29日11:09，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>下跌83.06點（或1%），暫報8223.69點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+3.29%</li><li>近 1 月：+15.25%</li><li>近 3 月：+15.46%</li><li>近 6 月：+44.79%</li><li>今年以來：+17.28%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)領跌。邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)下跌3.46%；安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)下跌3.39%；恩智浦半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NXPI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NXPI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NXPI-US</a>)下跌3%；安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)下跌2.79%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:C